{"word":"προσνίσσομαι","slug":"προσνίσσομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσνίσσομαι</b></el> <el>(doric <el>ποτι-νίσσομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to come</i> or <i>go to</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>; <el>θεοὺς θοίναις ποτιν.</el> <i>to approach</i> them with sacrifices, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to come against</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}